videos.description: Wendell Carter goes down after the play appearing to hurt his left ankle and had to leave the game.
videos.headline: Duke's Carter tweaks left ankle

videos.description: Justin Robinson comes in for Wendell Carter and hits a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Duke's Robinson knocks down corner triple

videos.description: Trevon Duval knocks down a corner three after a great look from Grayson Allen.
videos.headline: Allen gets into the lane to find an open Duval

videos.description: Wendell Carter Jr.'s ankle seems to be fine after throwing down a slam off of Marvin Bagley III's miss in transition.
videos.headline: Carter Jr. cleans up Bagley's miss with slam

videos.description: Juju Smith-Schuster makes an appearance and signs shirts to toss into the crowd at Pittsburgh.
videos.headline: Juju Smith-Schuster tosses out 'Pitt Is Lit' shirts

videos.description: Marvin Bagley III gets the steal and finishes on the other end, making a tough dunk look easy.
videos.headline: Bagley III throws it down in transition
